com.mathtastic.controller

Class SignInUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      • javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
        • com.mathtastic.controller.SignInUser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig

    @WebServlet(urlPatterns="/signInUser")
public class SignInUser
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
    SignInUser signs in an existing user. If user information does not match what is stored, the user is sent to signInFail.jsp where the user can attempt to sign in again. If the user information matches what is stored, the user session is set and the user is sent to index.jsp.
    See Also:
